    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lamps in which light is produced by an electric arc between two electrodes in a quartz bulb filled with xenon gas. They give off a constant high intensity light and are used in motion picture projection, flash photography, and serve as light sources in accelerated aging chambers.</Note_Text>
